OpenSand-live
=============

For more updated doc, please read the wiki : http://opensand.org/support/wiki/doku.php?id=opensand_live

Requirements
------------

In order to generate, you will need a Debian host with root access

Generation
----------

First, you'll need to have a complete arborescence, including qemu disks images and opensand debian packages. They are distributed out of the bazaar tree because of their huge size. They can be downloaded here : **TODO**. Install it simply by extracting it in the opensand-live directory.

Then, install live-build on your Debian system
  apt-get install live-build

Go in opensand-live directory then run
  lb config
  lb build

Known bugs
----------

 * ROHC support not included
 * Failsafe is selected by default in boot menu
